63 (5) Notwithstanding any provisions of this section to
64 the contrary, no person shall operate a passenger vehicle,
65 motor truck, or passenger bus which carries or transports
66 explosives or flammable liquids, as defined in Section
67 32-1-1.1, or hazardous wastes, as defined in Section
