73 operate the vehicle, truck, or bus at a rate of speed greater
74 than 55 miles per hour at any time unless a different maximum
75 rate of speed is authorized by the Governor under authority
76 granted in subdivision (6) or as provided in subdivision (7).
77 (6) The Governor may prescribe the maximum rate of
78 speed whenever a different rate of speed is required by
79 federal law in order for Alabama to receive federal funds for
